<A>__{rachel's aim follows vogel's lunge for the gateway... rachel's p.o.v there is a lurid flash of fireworks from nearby and for a moment we see vogel lit, about to make it to the gate and disappear forever... rachel fires. a single shot. and, improbably, incredibly, the tiny figure of vogel drops. rachel hangs over the banisters far above us, gun in hand, staring at us with disbelief.}
